SYNOPSIS: Yoga instructor Leann Carey hosts this video, which offers a simple, easy-to-follow introduction to the basics of yoga. Easy Yoga focuses on breathing exercises, which help to sooth and relax mind and body; basic yoga postures which help alleviate stress as they promote strength and flexibility; and exercises which will help novices warm up and cool down properly.
